Description:
In the central temple there is large stone statue of a snake coiled between the temple columns, instead of eyes the snake statue has two large rubies.

The statue is protected by several naga wardens with tridents that also protect an offering chest under the head of the statue.

Luckily you hid behind a column and no one has yet noticed your presence.
DescriptionAction: How do you want to proceed?
